data.description: Reduced for quick sale **3-Bedroom, 2-Bathroom Home with Spacious Bonus Room on a Sprawling 1 Acre Lot. Welcome to your new home sweet home in the highly sought-after Tuttle Public School District! Nestled on a picturesque one-acre lot, this lovingly-maintained 1960s gem boasts timeless charm, modern updates, and plenty of room to stretch out. This spacious home provides comfortable living for families of all sizes. Three well-appointed bedrooms offer ample closet space, while two updated bathrooms ensure convenience and comfort. Enjoy an additional 450 square feet of flexible space, perfect for a home office, playroom, or entertainment area. The possibilities are endless! New Hot Water Tank with Warranty: Worry-free mornings and evenings with a brand-new hot water tank backed by a warranty, ensuring years of reliable service. Energy-Efficient New Windows: Let natural light flood your living spaces through new windows that come with a lifetime transferable warranty, providing peace of mind and lower energy bills. New Air Conditioner: Stay cool during those warm Oklahoma summers with a new air conditioner, keeping your home comfortable all year round. Four-Car Carport: Protect your vehicles from the elements with a spacious four-car carport, perfect for cars, boats, or an RV. Expansive Yard: Embrace the joys of outdoor living on your generous one-acre lot. Create your dream garden, set up a play area for the kids, or simply relax in the open space. Tuttle Public School District: Enjoy the benefits of top-rated education in the highly-regarded Tuttle Public School District. This home offers the perfect blend of classic charm and modern convenience. You'll appreciate the peace and tranquility of the neighborhood while being just a short drive from shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Don't miss your chance to own this lovely piece of Tuttle's history. Schedule a showing today and make this beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house with bonus room your forever home!
